# Frontend Tools Search -- Windsurf Rules

## Project

A React + TypeScript single-page app for searching a list of frontend tools and technologies. Users type in a search box and see filtered results update in real time. Stack: React 18, TypeScript, Vite, TailwindCSS. No backend -- all data is mock with simulated async delay.

## What Needs Implementation

- src/hooks/useSearch.ts -- debounce (300 ms) + async searchItems call + stale-response prevention + unmount cleanup
- src/App.tsx -- replace placeholder div with conditional rendering

## Architecture Notes

- searchItems has variable latency -- race conditions are intentional test vectors
- Hook must handle: rapid typing, empty query, component unmount mid-request
- All state is local React state -- no context or external store

